{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/misc/adding-tailwindcss-to-gatsby/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Konnor's Blog","author":"Konnor Rogers"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"890e4bf5-1ab2-52aa-b31e-b48f62cd125a","excerpt":"Prerequisites Node (preferably 8+, I used 11.15.0)\nNpm (I used 6.7.0)\nGit (Gatsby requires Git to pull in starters) Note to windows users I wrote this tutorial…","html":"<h2>Prerequisites</h2>\n<p>Node (preferably 8+, I used 11.15.0)</br>\nNpm (I used 6.7.0)</br>\nGit (Gatsby requires Git to pull in starters)</br></p>\n<h2>Note to windows users</h2>\n<p>I wrote this tutorial with intent for Unix based users. Whenever you see the\ncommand <code class=\"language-text\">touch</code> it just means create a file and <code class=\"language-text\">mkdir</code> means create a directory (folder).\nAlso, I wrote filepaths with Unix based OS’es in mind.</p>\n<h2>TLDR</h2>\n<p>For the full tutorial below <a href=\"#full-tutorial\">Click here</a></p>\n<h3>For new projects</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"89934048644347350000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm install --global gatsby-cli\ngatsby new tailwind-gatsby-project\ncd tailwind-gatsby-project`, `89934048644347350000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --global gatsby-cli\ngatsby new tailwind-gatsby-project\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> tailwind-gatsby-project</code></pre></div>\n<h3>For new or existing projects</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"3729725700582276000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm install gatsby-plugin-postcss\nnpm install --save-dev tailwindcss\nnpx tailwind init\n\ntouch postcss.config.js\nmkdir src/styles\ntouch src/styles/tailwind.css`, `3729725700582276000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-plugin-postcss\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev tailwindcss\nnpx tailwind init\n\n<span class=\"token function\">touch</span> postcss.config.js\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> src/styles\n<span class=\"token function\">touch</span> src/styles/tailwind.css</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<strong>\n  1. Add gatsby-postcss-plugin to `./gatsby-config.js`\n</strong>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"6592860150946845000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./gatsby-config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  // Above code omitted for brevity\n  plugins: [\n    \\`gatsby-plugin-react-helmet\\`,\n    {\n      resolve: \\`gatsby-source-filesystem\\`,\n      options: {\n        name: \\`images\\`,\n        path: \\`\\${__dirname}/src/images\\`,\n      },\n    },\n    \\`gatsby-plugin-postcss\\`,\n    // Below code omitted for brevity\n  ],\n}`, `6592860150946845000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Above code omitted for brevity</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-react-helmet</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-source-filesystem</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>__dirname<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/src/images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-postcss</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Below code omitted for brevity</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>2. Add the following values to <code class=\"language-text\">./postcss.config.js</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"81539074453533540000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./postcss.config.js\n\nconst tailwindcss = require(\\`tailwindcss\\`)\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [tailwindcss(\\`./tailwind.config.js\\`), require(&quot;autoprefixer&quot;)],\n}`, `81539074453533540000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./postcss.config.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> tailwindcss <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">tailwindcss</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">tailwindcss</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">./tailwind.config.js</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"autoprefixer\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>3. Add tailwindcss directives to <code class=\"language-text\">./src/styles/tailwind.css</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"37449465326896700000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`/* ./src/styles/tailwind.css */\n@tailwind base\n@tailwind utilities;\n@tailwind components;`, `37449465326896700000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* ./src/styles/tailwind.css */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> base\n<span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> utilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> components<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>4. Add tailwindcss globally by importing it in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"26383906927816670000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./gatsby-browser.js\n\nimport &quot;./src/styles/tailwind.css&quot;`, `26383906927816670000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./gatsby-browser.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/styles/tailwind.css\"</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>5. Add a tailwind style to a an item in <code class=\"language-text\">./src/pages/index.js</code> to test that its working</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"87235152475558500000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./src/pages/index.js\n\n// Above code omitted for brevity\n<h1 className=&quot;bg-red-500&quot;>Hi people</h1>\n// Below code omitted for brevity`, `87235152475558500000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./src/pages/index.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Above code omitted for brevity</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bg-red-500\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Hi people<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Below code omitted for brevity</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>6. Start up your server</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"68112899594376856000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`gatsby develop`, `68112899594376856000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>7. Navigate to <code class=\"language-text\">localhost:8000</code> to see if Tailwind is working. That’s it!</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"full-tutorial> Full tutorial</h2>\n<p>If you already have a Gatsby project feel free to skip ahead to the\n<a href=\"#adding-to-an-existing-project\">Adding to an existing project section</a></p>\n<p><strong>1. First, start by creating a new Gatsby project. The easiest way to do so is:</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"82336139142379110000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm install --global gatsby-cli`, `82336139142379110000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --global gatsby-cli</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>2. Then to create a new project:</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"49417875191631480000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`gatsby new tailwind-gatsby-project`, `49417875191631480000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gatsby new tailwind-gatsby-project</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p>This will create a new Gatsby project called <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind-gatsby-project</code></p>\n<p><strong>3. Now, navigate into the project directory:</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"17712670239310492000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`cd tailwind-gatsby-project`, `17712670239310492000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> tailwind-gatsby-project</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p>Make sure running <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby develop</code> works before moving on.</p>\n<h2 id=\"adding-to-an-existing-project\"> Adding to an existing project</h2>\n<p><strong>4. Add <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-plugin-postcss/\">gatsby-plugin-postcss</a> package</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"25917041647877670000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm install gatsby-plugin-postcss`, `25917041647877670000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gatsby-plugin-postcss</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>5. Add gatsby-postcss-plugin to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"29462804820456202000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./gatsby-config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  // Above code omitted for brevity\n  plugins: [\n    \\`gatsby-plugin-react-helmet\\`,\n    {\n      resolve: \\`gatsby-source-filesystem\\`,\n      options: {\n        name: \\`images\\`,\n        path: \\`\\${__dirname}/src/images\\`,\n      },\n    },\n    \\`gatsby-plugin-postcss\\`,\n    // Below code omitted for brevity\n  ],\n}`, `29462804820456202000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Above code omitted for brevity</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-react-helmet</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-source-filesystem</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>__dirname<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/src/images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-postcss</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Below code omitted for brevity</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>6. Create a <code class=\"language-text\">postcss.config.js</code> file in the root directory</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"66845459784592530000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`touch postcss.config.js`, `66845459784592530000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">touch</span> postcss.config.js</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>7. Add the following content to <code class=\"language-text\">postcss.config.js</code>:</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"15658232074416855000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./postcss.config.js\n\nconst tailwindcss = require(\\`tailwindcss\\`)\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [tailwindcss(\\`./tailwind.config.js\\`), require(&quot;autoprefixer&quot;)],\n}`, `15658232074416855000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./postcss.config.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> tailwindcss <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">tailwindcss</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">tailwindcss</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">./tailwind.config.js</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"autoprefixer\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>8. Add the <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation\">TailwindCSS</a> package</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"63211593506139914000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm install --save-dev tailwindcss`, `63211593506139914000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev tailwindcss</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>9. Create a directory called in <code class=\"language-text\">styles</code> in the <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> directory</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"32605736209763013000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`mkdir src/styles`, `32605736209763013000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> src/styles</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>10. Create a stylesheet called <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind.css</code> in the <code class=\"language-text\">src/styles</code> directory</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"9595231742311850000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`touch src/styles/tailwind.css`, `9595231742311850000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">touch</span> src/styles/tailwind.css</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>11. Add the following content:</strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"64324061663103934000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`/* ./src/styles/tailwind.css */\n\n@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;`, `64324061663103934000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* ./src/styles/tailwind.css */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> base<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> components<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> utilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>12. To add tailwind styles globally, import it in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"14565737619826758000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`import &quot;./src/styles/tailwind.css&quot;`, `14565737619826758000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/styles/tailwind.css\"</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p>Everything should now be working! However, we currently have no way of telling.\nLets add a tailwind style to the index page.</p>\n<p><strong>13. Add a tailwind style to the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h1&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</code> tag in <code class=\"language-text\">src/pages/index.js</code></strong></p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"64431919122700830000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// ./src/pages/index.js\n\n// Above code omitted for brevity\n<h1 className=&quot;bg-red-500&quot;>Hi people</h1>\n// Below code omitted for brevity`, `64431919122700830000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./src/pages/index.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Above code omitted for brevity</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bg-red-500\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Hi people<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Below code omitted for brevity</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<p><strong>14. Run <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-develop</code></strong></p>\n<p>You should now see a red background for the text that says “Hi people”. This\nlets you know tailwind is working as expected! Hope this worked for you getting\nTailwindCSS setup in Gatsby.</p>\n<p>Make sure if you still have the server from earlier running to shut it down and\nrestart it.</p>\n<h2>Links</h2>\n<h3>My github repo using Tailwind and Gatsby</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ParamagicDev/tailwind-gatsby-project\">Reference Repository</a></p>\n<h3>Gatsby</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org\">Gatsby</a></br>\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/tailwind-css/\">Gatsby + Tailwind tutorial</a></br>\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/tutorial/part-two/#creating-global-styles-with-standard-css-files\">Using CSS in Gatsby</a></br></p>\n<h3>Tailwind</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/\">TailwindCSS</a></br>\n<a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation\">TailwindCSS Installation</a></br></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Adding tailwindcss to a Gatsby project","date":"January 20, 2020","description":"Details on how to add tailwindcss to a Gatsby project."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/misc/adding-tailwindcss-to-gatsby/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/setting-up-gatsby-with-docker/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Setting up a Gatsby project with Docker"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/adding-emotion-typescript-and-jest/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Adding Emotion, Typescript, and Jest to Gatsby"}}}}}